{
  "stem": "17001.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we get back to our lager my sister Elizabeth and-- and my cousin, their eyes is cried out because they were told that we were bombed down, and goodbye sisters.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No more sisters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said to her, thank God we are back and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Meantime in the big commotion because they were bombing on the lager also, she managed to steal a small little [HUNGARIAN] with all beautiful delicious potato soup.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we started eating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And naturally there are other girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They start to come over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's no-- no privacy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can't do too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we gave some of them-- some of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our stomach was so puffed up, so full.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Meantime when it came Sunday, Sunday they didn't take us to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a chance to relax or some time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before Christmas, the Blockalteste and the Lageralteste were teaching the girls how to perform, how to sing different German songs to entertain the German crew.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Meantime the Lageralteste befriended the Oberscharfuehrer, and they became very good friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, there was another [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] woman soldier, the-- I can't think of the name of it now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was in love with the Oberscharfuehrer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was jealous of Lola.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a very big rivalry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the-- the Oberscharfuehrer had to be-- go-- had to be sent away for something, had to attend some kind of a meeting or something, then the-- the-- this German woman, she was the head.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she made us kneel in the snow, in the ice, all day long to-- to get her frustration out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At one occasion, I was able to sneak near to the kitchen, and I bend in through the window and I picked up one of these leek.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
